c CSNF for compose_cycle.tlsf
p csnf 2 0 0 0
m semantics Mealy
b 0 solved definition
bc 0 c0
dec 0 o1 a && o2
cert 0 definition_decoder
cl 0 G (o1 <-> a && o2)
b 1 solved definition
bc 1 c1
dec 1 o2 b && o1
cert 1 definition_decoder
cl 1 G (o2 <-> b && o1)
do o1
do o2
composition: residual=1 conflicts=1 accepted=1
x decoder-cycle o1 block 0
